<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2966] Glyphs overlapping in rendering</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2966</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See attachment, this is reduced (but uncompressed) from the original pdf. All the glyphs render at about the same position. I did some tracing, the widths of the glyphs are about the same as the values within TJ.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12863097">PDFBOX-2966</key>
            <summary>Glyphs overlapping in rendering</summary>
